sources.description:
Watching Amber - After the death of Amber's ex boyfriend Paul, she's determined to move on and continue with the new love of her life Chad. Even though Amber tries to put her past behind her, she's stalked by a mental neighbor who is crazy for her and is determined to eliminate all competition at any cost
